raw_text = "~ start
## 2pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Valerie: Heyyy you 🥰
Valerie: It's Valerie!! 😇
Valerie: img: valerie/9
Valerie: You remember me riiight?
Player: How did you get my number? 😅
Valerie: Silly, all frat boys are basically easy access
Valerie: I've had my eye on you for a whiiile now
Valerie: Sorry I was sooo busy 😩
Valerie: But I'll make it up to you 🥰
Valerie: You even realize how yummy you look?
Player: Huh, yummy? 😀
Valerie: Mhmm... All tied up closely with THAT girl 🙄
Valerie: It seriously makes me giddy
Player: 😅
Valerie: Mabel, riiight? Your girlfriend
Valerie: Suuuper cute, I loooove her hair and her adorable frame 🥰
Valerie: And how she gets to go on dates so often
Valerie: You take her out literally EVERY weekend 😩
Valerie: You're not missing a moment with her, are you?
Valerie: Do you have any idea how rare a boy like you is??
Player: How..??
Valerie: ☺️
Valerie: Devoted boys are my absolute favorite kind of flower to pick and wear in my hair 🥰
Valerie: And I want all that honey for myself 🤭
- That's not going to happen
	Player: That's not going to happen
	Valerie: Honestly.. That just makes me want you more 😬😍
- You're actually insane 😅
	Player: You're actually insane 😅
	Valerie: The cute kind though, riiight?? 🥰🥰
	Valerie: More exciting than that boring ol Mabel
Valerie: How many foot jobs has she given you?
Player: 😶
Valerie: My guess is 0
Valerie: Anywayyy, let's talk about Sunday 🤭
Valerie: That's your special little date day with Mabel, isn't it
Valerie: Don't even ask how I know. Homework 😇
Player: 😳
Valerie: So here's the fun part, listen close
Valerie: This Sunday? You're not taking her out
Valerie: You're taking ME instead 🥰
Valerie: I'll make it sooo worth it, promise promise 🥺
- I can't do that
	Player: I can't do that
	Valerie: Mmmm, a challenge 😍
	Valerie: That's okay, I'm a verryy patient girl
	Valerie: I always get my boy in the end 😘
	Valerie: See you soon, cutie
- If you insist 😅 [#brownheart]
	set Story.brown_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Date4Val\"
	Player: If you insist 😅
	Valerie: I do!!
	Valerie: I KNEW you had good taste hehe 🥰🥰
	Valerie: Good boys get rewarded, and you're a good boy hehe
	Valerie: img: valerie/10
	Player: 😳
	Valerie: 😉
	Valerie: It's going to be the best date you'll ever have
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
